"title": "4456: grain",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4456: grain",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The seed of cereals. Together with wine and oil, it was one of the three basic commodities in biblical times. Grain offerings were central to Israelite religion and tithes and firstfruits of grain were also given to God.</p>\n<h2>Grain was a basic foodstuff</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:12-Deut7:13\">DEU 7:12–7:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:13-Deut11:15\">DEU 11:13–11:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:49-Deut28:51\">DEU 28:49–28:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut33:28\">DEU 33:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:14\">RUT 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:17\">1SA 17:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:18\">1SA 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:3\">NEH 5:1–5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:10-Neh5:11\">NEH 5:10–5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Harvesting and threshing grain</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:4\">DEU 25:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:9-Lev19:10\">LEV 19:9–19:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:19\">DEU 24:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:11\">JDG 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:2-Ruth2:9\">RUT 2:2–2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:15-Ruth2:17\">RUT 2:15–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:2\">RUT 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>Storing grain</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:47-Gen41:49\">GEN 41:47–41:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:33-Gen41:36\">GEN 41:33–41:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:27-2Chr32:28\">2CH 32:27–32:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:26\">PRO 11:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:26\">JER 50:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:17\">JOL 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a></p>\n<h2>Tithes and firstfruits of grain</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:30\">LEV 27:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:9-Lev23:11\">LEV 23:9–23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:17\">DEU 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:23\">DEU 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:1-Deut18:5\">DEU 18:1–18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:4-2Chr31:5\">2CH 31:4–31:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:37-Neh10:39\">NEH 10:37–10:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:12\">NEH 13:12</a></p>\n<h2>The grain offering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev2:1-Lev2:16\">LEV 2:1–2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:14-Lev6:23\">LEV 6:14–6:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15-Lev23:16\">LEV 23:15–23:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:11-Num5:28\">NUM 5:11–5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:1-Num15:12\">NUM 15:1–15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:64\">1KI 8:64</a></p>\n<h2>Barley as grain</h2>\n<h3>The cultivation of barley</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:30\">2SA 14:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:31\">EXO 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:16\">LEV 27:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7-Deut8:9\">DEU 8:7–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:22\">RUT 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:17-Ruth2:18\">RUT 2:17–2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:23\">RUT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:2\">RUT 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:9\">2SA 21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:13\">1CH 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:38-Job31:40\">JOB 31:38–31:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:24-Isa28:25\">ISA 28:24–28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:11\">JOL 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Trade in barley</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:2\">HOS 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1\">2KI 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:16-2Kgs7:18\">2KI 7:16–7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:10\">2CH 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:15-2Chr2:16\">2CH 2:15–2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:5\">2CH 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:19\">EZK 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:6\">REV 6:6</a></p>\n<h3>The consumption of barley</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:9-Ezek4:12\">EZK 4:9–4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:15-Ruth3:17\">RUT 3:15–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:27-2Sam17:29\">2SA 17:27–17:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:28\">1KI 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:42-2Kgs4:44\">2KI 4:42–4:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:8\">JER 41:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:5-John6:13\">JHN 6:5–6:13</a></p>\n<h3>Offerings of barley</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:13\">EZK 45:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:11-Num5:15\">NUM 5:11–5:15</a></p>\n<h2>Other kinds of grain</h2>\n<h3>Corn</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:16\">PSA 72:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:7\">GEN 37:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:13\">PSA 65:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:7\">HOS 14:7</a></p>\n<h3>Millet</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:9\">EZK 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Spelt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:24-Isa28:25\">ISA 28:24–28:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:22-Exod9:32\">EXO 9:22–9:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek4:9\">EZK 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Wheat</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:17\">EZK 27:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:11\">JDG 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:5\">2CH 27:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:14\">PSA 147:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:24\">JHN 12:24</a></p>\n<h2>Allusions to grain in the teaching of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:26-Mark4:29\">MRK 4:26–4:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:1-Matt13:9\">MAT 13:1–13:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:3-Mark4:8\">MRK 4:3–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:18-Matt13:23\">MAT 13:18–13:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:14-Mark4:20\">MRK 4:14–4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:24-Matt13:30\">MAT 13:24–13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:36-Matt13:43\">MAT 13:36–13:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:13-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:13–12:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:1-Luke16:9\">LUK 16:1–16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:35\">LUK 17:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:24\">JHN 12:24</a></p>",
